"Bank all %s Goldkluut."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Deep Gold Mine
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1335 input:1335 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"'A land whose stones are iron, and out of whose hills you can dig copper.'"
msgstr ""
"»En Land, dessen Steen järn is, un ut de Hügel kannst du Kupfer gräven.«"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Deep Gold Mine
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1339 input:1339 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Digs gold ore out of the ground in mountain terrain. This mine reaches the "
"deepest veins."
msgstr ""
"Grafft in Bargen Goldkluut ut de Grund. Deeses Bargwark kummt bit in de "
"deepsten Aders."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Granite Mine
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1348 input:1348 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"'Solomon's builders cut the great stones to lay the foundation of the "
"temple.'"
msgstr ""
"»Salomos Baumeister schnitt de großen Steen, um de Grondslag von den Tempel "
"to legen.«"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Granite Mine
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1352 input:1352 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Carves granite out of the rock in mountain terrain."
msgstr "Grafft in Bargen Flint ut de Grund."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Hebrew production site: Granite Mine
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1354 input:1354 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "It cannot be enhanced."
msgstr "’t kann nich utbaut worden."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Hebrew production site: Granite Mine
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1356 input:1356 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"If the food supply is steady, this mine can produce granite in %s on average."
msgstr ""
"Wenn de Spiesen to rechter Tied ankomen, produzeert deeses Bargwark dör de "
"Bank all %s Flint."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Threshing Floor
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1363 input:1363 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "'Ornan was threshing wheat on the threshing floor.'"
msgstr "»Ornan wurrt Weiz op de Dreschföhr dreschen.«"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Threshing Floor
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1365 input:1365 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "First Book of Chronicles"
msgstr "Erstes Buch der Chroniken"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Threshing Floor
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1367 input:1367 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Threshes harvested wheat into wheat grains."
msgstr "Dösket arnt Weitschoven, um Weitkoorn to winnen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Vineyard
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1374 input:1374 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "'Noah began to be a man of the soil, and he planted a vineyard.'"
msgstr "»Noah began een Mann von de Boden to wüüsen, un he plant en Weinberg.«"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Vineyard
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1378 input:1378 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Cultivates grapevines and harvests grapes."
msgstr "Plant un arnt Wiendruven."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew training site: Training Camp
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1387 input:1387 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"'Blessed be the Lord my Rock, who trains my hands for war and my fingers for "
"battle.'"
msgstr ""
"»Gesegnet sei de Herr, min Fels, wo min Hänn för Krich un min Finger för "
"Kampf trainiert.«"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew training site: Training Camp
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1389 input:1389 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Psalm 144"
msgstr "Psalm 144"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew training site: Training Camp, part 1
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1392 input:1392 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Trains soldiers in 'Attack', 'Health' and 'Evade'."
msgstr "Lehrt Soldaten »Angriff«, »Gesundheid« un »Utwieken«."

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew training site: Training Camp, part 2
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1394 input:1394 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Equips the soldiers with all necessary weapons and armor parts."
msgstr "Rüst de Soldaten mit all nödigen Wapen un Wapenrocken ut."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Hebrew training site: Training Camp
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1397 input:1397 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Hebrew soldiers cannot be trained in 'Defense' and will remain at their "
"initial level."
msgstr ""
"Hebräisk Soldaten könen keene »Verteidigung« öven un blieven immer up hör "
"Anfang-Stand."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for a Hebrew training site: Training Camp
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1399 input:1399 standard
#, lua-format
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"If all needed wares are delivered in time, a training camp can train one new "
"soldier in attack, health and evade to the final level in %s on average."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew military site: Small Tent
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1408 input:1408 standard
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "'How good are your tents, O Jacob, your dwelling places, O Israel!'"
msgstr "»Wie good sind dien Zelte, o Jakob, dien Wunnplaatsen, o Israel!«"

